#. <section class="sutta" id="sn15.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Puggalasutta → ekapuggalasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn15.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Puggalasutta"
msgstr "10. A Single Person"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak Mountain."

msgctxt "sn15.10:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn15.10:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicants!”"

msgctxt "sn15.10:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "sn15.10:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:2.1"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe …"
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. …"

# BB adds “hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving” here, apparently by mistake.
msgctxt "sn15.10:2.2"
msgid "ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kappaṃ sandhāvato saṃsarato siyā evaṃ mahā aṭṭhikaṅkalo aṭṭhipuñjo aṭṭhirāsi yathāyaṃ vepullo pabbato, sace saṃhārako assa, sambhatañca na vinasseyya."
msgstr "One person roaming and transmigrating for an eon would amass a heap of bones the size of this Mount Vepulla, if they were gathered together and not lost."

msgctxt "sn15.10:2.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn15.10:2.4"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe …"
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.10:2.5"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn15.10:3.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:4.1"
msgid "“Ekassekena kappena,"
msgstr "“If the bones of a single person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:4.2"
msgid "puggalassaṭṭhisañcayo;"
msgstr "for a single eon were gathered up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:4.3"
msgid "Siyā pabbatasamo rāsi,"
msgstr "they’d make a pile the size of a mountain:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:4.4"
msgid "iti vuttaṃ mahesinā."
msgstr "so said the great hermit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:5.1"
msgid "So kho panāyaṃ akkhāto,"
msgstr "And this is declared to be"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:5.2"
msgid "vepullo pabbato mahā;"
msgstr "as huge as Mount Vepulla,"

# Contra BB, Mount vepulla is, it seems, south of Gijjhakuta, so uttara must mean “higher” here, which makes sense in context.
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:5.3"
msgid "Uttaro gijjhakūṭassa,"
msgstr "higher than the Vulture’s Peak"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:5.4"
msgid "magadhānaṃ giribbaje."
msgstr "in the Magadhan mountain range."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:6.1"
msgid "Yato ca ariyasaccāni,"
msgstr "But then, with right understanding,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:6.2"
msgid "sammappaññāya passati;"
msgstr "a person sees the noble truths—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:6.3"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ dukkhasamuppādaṃ,"
msgstr "suffering, suffering’s origin,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:6.4"
msgid "dukkhassa ca atikkamaṃ;"
msgstr "suffering’s transcendence,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:6.5"
msgid "Ariyaṃ caṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ,"
msgstr "and the noble eightfold path"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:6.6"
msgid "dukkhūpasamagāminaṃ."
msgstr "that leads to the stilling of suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.186"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:7.1"
msgid "Sa sattakkhattuṃparamaṃ,"
msgstr "After roaming on seven times at most,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:7.2"
msgid "sandhāvitvāna puggalo;"
msgstr "that person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:7.3"
msgid "Dukkhassantakaro hoti,"
msgstr "makes an end of suffering,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:7.4"
msgid "sabbasaṃyojanakkhayā”ti."
msgstr "with the ending of all fetters.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.10:7.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.10:7.6"
msgid "Paṭhamo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.10:8.1"
msgid "Tiṇakaṭṭhañca pathavī,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:8.2"
msgid "assu khīrañca pabbataṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:8.3"
msgid "Sāsapā sāvakā gaṅgā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn15.10:8.4"
msgid "daṇḍo ca puggalena cāti."
msgstr ""
